mamluk"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7xu","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":22096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/27\/rahmah-sheep-slaughter\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Have mercy on the sheep, do not slaughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurra ibn Iyas reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I would have slaughtered a sheep but I had mercy on it.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you had mercy on the sheep, Allah will have mercy on you twice.\u201d Source: al-Adab\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29330,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/sahabah-said-when-praised\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Humility: What the companions said when praised","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Adi ibn Artah reported: When a man among the companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was praised for his righteousness, he would say, \u201cO Allah, do not blame me for what they say and forgive me for what they do not know!\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/04\/worst-muslims-arrogant\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Worst Muslims brag, boast, speak too much","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe worst of my nation are the garrulous, the braggarts,\u00a0and the pompous. The best of my nation are those with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1308 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9944,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/abu-huraira-speck-plank-eye\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":3},"title":"Abu Huraira on Hypocrisy: You ignore the plank in your own eye?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-Asim reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cOne of you looks at the speck in his brother\u2019s eye while he ignores the plank or log in his own eye.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 592 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/why-servants-despair\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Laughter: Why make My servants despair?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to a group of his companions while they were laughing and talking. The Prophet said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, if you knew what I knew, you would laugh little and weep often.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10054,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/26\/ammar-slaves-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28984,"position":5},"title":"Ammar on Slaves: Allah retaliates for slaves unjustly abused","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymun ibn Abi Shabib reported: 'Ammar ibn Yasir, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNone of you strikes his slave unjustly but that the slave will be granted retaliation on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 181 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0634\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/28984","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=28984"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/28984\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=28984"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=28984"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=28984"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}